## Any [[rule]] that must or should be obeyed, concerning [[behaviour]]s and their [[consequence]]s. {{q|Compare {{m|en|mores}}.}}
##: {{ux|en|"Do unto others as you wish them to do unto you" is a good '''law''' to follow. &nbsp; the '''law''' of self-preservation}}
